column1: Traffic reports will resume Wednesday January 25 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: Traffic Alert for I-75N / I-64W at the Northern Split:
column4: The roadway is shutdown at the northern split until further notice due to an overturned mobile home and trailer located past the split.

column3: Traffic Alert for I-75N / I-64W at the Northern Split:
